    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nCurrently, the default behavior of `'spellfile'` is to use the first directory in the runtimepath that is writable (which generally is `stdpath('config')` I think?). Using the XDG data dir is a stronger, more expectable default. It is also more in line with the XDG base dir spec than using the config dir.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nBy default the files with added words are placed in `stdpath('data')/spell`.",
